channel.title: Server tracker
channel.description:
Just a question, if you drop to 99 percent, is it possible to reach 100 ever again?
Mathematically I believe it's not, but I was told by someone it's possible.
True/false?
Mine's been up since 4/11, and it dropped to 99 percent just last night, is it possible to get back to 100?
